OOC: Okay guys, who's Autobots are here, everyone should try to respond.

Pacifix neared the base, contemplating the things he had learned. If he
ever made it back to Cybertron, he was going to thuroughly investigate
this Gamma, in any way he could. He roared to a stop near the entrance
to thier ship, Hoist stood there waiting for them. The rear transport
part opened up for Gesper to exit. Hoist stood waiting to greet the
robot.

"Welcome to Autobot headquarters." Pacifix said warmly, seperating from
the rear part of his vehicle mode, then transforming into his robot
mode.
